snippet.title: Streets At Midnight (itch.io Game)
snippet.description:
Get it here: https://falling-ash-games.itch.io/streets-at-midnight

The trailer for Streets At Midnight! Inspired by various shooters in the wave survival genre, I set out to make my own. Play in two different game modes across 3 maps as you struggle to survive the undead!
